\title{Infinity Operads}

\taxon{skill}

\meta{trit}{0}

\meta{description}{"∞-Operads for pairwise/tritwise Cat# interactions with lazy ACSet materialization unifying effective, realizability, and Grothendieck topoi via dendroidal Segal spaces."}

\subtree{
\title{∞-Operads Skill (ERGODIC 0)}
\blockquote{*"The dendroidal nerve carries operads to ∞-operads exactly as the simplicial nerve carries categories to ∞-categories."* — Cisinski-Moerdijk}

\p{\strong{Trit}: 0 (ERGODIC) \strong{Color}: #26D826 (Green) \strong{Role}: Coordinator/Transporter \strong{XIP}: Dendroidal (Ω-set) → Cat# horizontal morphism}

\subtree{
\title{Core Insight: Pairwise = Bicomodule, Tritwise = Equipment Tensor}
\pre{\startverb
| Interaction Type | Cat# Structure | Operad View | Lazy ACSet |
|------------------|----------------|-------------|------------|
| **Pairwise** | Bicomodule composition in Prof | Binary operation | `JOIN` on demand |
| **Tritwise** | Equipment tensor ⊗ (GF(3) balanced) | Ternary tree grafting | Materialized view |
| **N-ary** | ∞-operad algebra evaluation | Dendroidal composition | Recursive CTE |
